name: WOOF! & MEOW! Key Chains
description:
Do you want to remember your babies wherever you are? Going through your busy day, then all of a sudden, you remember an adorable thing they did that week, and despite your busy schedule, just stop and smile? :)

Get a WOOF! & MEOW! Key Chain with your baby's name on it :) You can use them for your car keys, for your house keys, or even as your bag chains :) 

You will remember your doggies and kitties wherever you are :o)

For doggies, their names are placed in a doggy bone (their favorite treat!) surrounded by specially etched doggy claws :) 

For kitties, their names are etched on a heart (showing your love of course) surrounded by specially etched kitty claws :) 

You can even choose whether you want the ring in the center of the bone, or in the side :) :) :) 

Very personalized. Very premium... :)

name: MEOW! Personalized Kitty Tags
description:

They are not only cute, they are essential. I've heard so many stories of cats that love to explore. Don't you want to make sure your kitty doesn't get lost, and goes home to you? It is definitely worth the comfort of knowing that your beloved baby will never get lost :)

Order a MEOW! Kitty Tag for your baby now :o)

name: MEOW! Personalized Kitty Bowls
description:
Your kitty deserves to be treated like royalty. Give your kitty a bowl with his name on it :)

The MEOW! Kitty Tag is a brass plated nameplate shaped like a heart (I know how much you love your kitties!) that is attached by gold screws to your kitty's bowl. 

The name of your kitty is surrounded by kitty claws :) :) :)

Get one for your kitty now :)
